sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant vLLM_M as vLLM Model Server<br/>(Metrics)
    participant vLLM_KV as vLLM Model Server<br/>(KV Events 5556/TCP ZMQ)
    participant Sidecar as P/D Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as Prefiller Pod
    participant Decoder as Decoder (vLLM)<br/>8001/TCP
    participant UDS as UDS Tokenizer<br/>Unix Domain Socket

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over EPP,K8s: Startup: Controller Watches
        EPP->>K8s: Watch InferencePool CRs<br/>SA token auth
        EPP->>K8s: Watch Pod resources<br/>(matching pool selector)
        EPP->>K8s: Watch InferenceObjective CRs
        EPP->>K8s: Watch InferenceModelRewrite CRs
        K8s-->>EPP: Resource events (add/update/delete)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over EPP,vLLM_KV: Background: Metrics & KV Cache Collection
        loop Every refresh-metrics-interval
            EPP->>vLLM_M: GET /metrics (HTTP/HTTPS)<br/>Queue depth, KV cache %, LoRA info
            vLLM_M-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics
        end
        vLLM_KV-)EPP: ZMQ PUB/SUB KV cache events<br/>5556/TCP (continuous)
        EPP->>EPP: Update KV cache index<br/>(llm-d-kv-cache library)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Inference Request Routing (EPP)
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
        GW->>EPP: ext_proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC streaming 9002/TCP
        EPP->>UDS: Tokenize prompt<br/>gRPC over UDS
        UDS-->>EPP: Token IDs
        EPP->>EPP: Run scheduling pipeline<br/>Filters → Scorers → Pickers
        Note over EPP: Select optimal endpoint based on:<br/>- KV cache prefix match<br/>- Queue depth<br/>- Load balancing<br/>- Priority/admission
        EPP-->>GW: ProcessingResponse<br/>(target endpoint in headers)
        GW->>Decoder: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000
        Decoder-->>GW: Inference response
        GW-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over GW,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated P/D Inference (Sidecar)
        GW->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP<br/>(EPP set x-prefill-host header)
        Sidecar->>Sidecar: Validate prefill target<br/>(SSRF allowlist check)
        Sidecar->>Prefiller: Forward prefill request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Optional TLS)
        Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response<br/>(KV cache transfer params)
        Note over Sidecar: KV cache transfer via connector:<br/>NIXL V2 / Shared Storage / SGLang
        Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward decode request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8001/TCP
        Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streamed inference response
        Sidecar-->>GW: Streamed response
        GW-->>Client: Streamed response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
        Note over vLLM_KV,EPP: Flow 3: KV Cache Event Subscription
        vLLM_KV-)EPP: KV cache block events<br/>ZMQ PUB/SUB 5556/TCP
        EPP->>EPP: Update prefix cache index<br/>for precise scoring
    end
